[{"Id": 1013074, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Ziyarat of the Paternal Aunts (Father’s sisters) of the Holy Prophet (s). The graves of these ladies: Safiya and Ateka and that of Hazrat Abbas’s (a) mother, Ummul Baneen are near each other in Baqi. Safiya was a very brave and virtuous lady and she was also a poetess. She accepted Islam in the initial stage. She paid allegiance to the Prophet (s) and migrated to Madina with him. She was also present in the Battles of Ohod and Khandaq. She passed away in 20 AH. at the age of 73. Ateka was a very honest lady. She is included amongst the companions of the Prophet (s). Recite the Ziyarat of these two aunts of the Holy Prophet in the following words…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Rasool-e-Khuda (s) ki fufi ki ziyarat. Yeh khaatoon Safiya, Ateka aur Hazrat Abbas (a) ki waaleda, Ummul Baneen ki qabr aas paas mein isi Baqi mein hai. Safiya bohot bahadur aur parhez gar khaatoon thi aur woh shahyar bhi thi. Unho ne Islam bahot jald qabool kiya. Woh Rasool (s) ke haath par baiy’at karte huwe Madina hijrat ki. Woh janghe Ohad aur Khandaq mein shaamil thi. Woh is duniya se 20 Hijri mein rukhsat huwi. Ateka bohot hi imaandar khaatoon thi. Woh Rasool (s) ke sahaabiyo’n mein shumaar hai. In dono phuphiyo’n ki ziyarat is tarah se hai…", "UrduDescription": "پیغمبر اسلامؐ کی دو پھو پھیاں جناب صفیہ بنت عبد المطلب اور جناب عاتکہ بنت عبد المطلب بھی جنت البقیع میں مدفون ہیںان با عظمت خواتین کی زیارت کے لئے کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenS